[section#thread.coord
    [:en] Coordination types
    [:zh_CN] 协作类型
]

[para]
[:en] This subclause describes various concepts related to thread coordination,
and defines the coordination types [`latch] and [`barrier].
[:zh_CN] 本子条款描述多种与线程协作相关的概念，并定义了协作类型 [`latch] 和
[`barrier]。

[:en] These types facilitate concurrent computation performed by a number of
threads.
[:zh_CN] 这些类型有助于由大量线程实施的并发计算。

[include thread.latch]

[include thread.barrier]
